OL,3,CGrandmother 'frustrated' over British
OL,4,CGas debt she refuses to pay online
OL,6,FA grandmother says she suffers from
OL,7,F"sleepless nights" due to a debt she
OL,8,Fowes to British Gas who have yet to
OL,9,Fsend her bills in the post after
OL,10,Fmoving her communications online.
OL,12,FPat Arrend, 84, from Brighton, Sussex
OL,13,Frefuses to pay her energy bills online
OL,14,Fas she does not have access to the
OL,15,Finternet.
OL,17,FBritish Gas went paperless last year
OL,18,Fand Pat told the company that she can
OL,19,Fonly settle bills in person at the
OL,20,FPost Office.
