OL,3,CGrandmother 'frustrated' over British
OL,4,CGas debt she refuses to pay online
OL,6,FShe's now racked up #1,400 in debt and
OL,7,Fhas been chased by solicitors working
OL,8,Ffor the firm.
OL,10,FPat said: "Up until they went
OL,11,Fpaperless, bills were paid on time. No
OL,12,Fproblems at all.
OL,14,F"I'm trying to chase them up every
OL,15,Ftime. I've been promised so many times
OL,16,Fthat I will get them in the post and
OL,17,Fit's just never happened.
