OL,3,CGrandmother 'frustrated' over British
OL,4,CGas debt she refuses to pay online
OL,6,F"I have never owed money, never, and
OL,7,Fto reach 84 and have this going on all
OL,8,Fby a company like British Gas, what's
OL,9,Fthe matter with them?"
OL,11,FThe letters that Pat has received in
OL,12,Fthe post have warned of penalties for
OL,13,Fthe missed payments.
OL,15,FPat said: "I've got a family, I can
OL,16,Fget them involved but then I've got to
OL,17,Fgive them all my details, no it's not
OL,18,Fon.
