OL,3,CGrandmother 'frustrated' over British
OL,4,CGas debt she refuses to pay online
OL,6,F"I lose my sense of independence and I
OL,7,Fjust become a non-entity which is
OL,8,Fhappening too often with our age group
OL,9,Fand it's not on."
OL,11,FThe dispute highlights the digital
OL,12,Fdivide, where not everyone knows how
OL,13,For wants to use technology.
OL,15,FAge UK estimates that one in three
OL,16,Fover 60s, around 5 million people,
OL,17,Ffind life much harder now because more
OL,18,Fof it is online.
