OL,6,FFive in 10 people feel frustrated when
OL,7,Fdirected to online services instead of
OL,8,Fbeing able to speak to someone on the
OL,9,Fphone.
OL,11,FWhile four in 10 believe the push
OL,12,Ftowards online technology is ageist.
OL,14,FBritish Gas says most of its millions
OL,15,Fof customers choose paperless billing
OL,16,Fbecause it's safer, faster and more
OL,17,Fenvironmentally friendly but customers
OL,18,Fcan still choose to receive bills
OL,19,Fthrough the post.
