OL,6,FRegarding Pat's case, British Gas
OL,7,Fsaid: "We've spoken with Ms Arrend to
OL,8,Fapologise and have reassured her that
OL,9,Fshe is now getting paper bills through
OL,10,Fthe post.
OL,12,F"We remain in touch and will be
OL,13,Foffering a goodwill gesture in light
OL,14,Fof her experience."
OL,16,FPat argues that she's not received any
OL,17,Frecent communication, but British Gas
OL,18,Finsists that it has reached out.
